WEBVTT


00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.240
I feel like the internet needs some basic rules of engagement

00:00:02.241 --> 00:00:05.520
making tens of thousands of people think that you are in a crisis situation

00:00:05.521 --> 00:00:07.480
or you or your children's life might be in state

00:00:07.481 --> 00:00:09.680
because your husband is going through a mental health crisis

00:00:09.681 --> 00:00:12.440
when in reality you're just telling a story about what happened a few months ago

00:00:12.441 --> 00:00:13.920
because you want this to go out

00:00:13.921 --> 00:00:16.991
you know to as many people as possible to raise awareness and help

00:00:16.992 --> 00:00:18.480
 it really rubs me the wrong way

00:00:18.481 --> 00:00:21.320
it's obviously not the worst thing that someone has done for clicks and views

00:00:21.321 --> 00:00:25.080
however it's really difficult to watch people continuously cross boundaries of

00:00:25.081 --> 00:00:26.040
like what is normal

00:00:26.041 --> 00:00:27.720
rational and sane just for a platform

00:00:27.721 --> 00:00:30.440
just for some views it's getting really frustrating to watch

00:00:30.441 --> 00:00:32.720
just like lack of basic fucking decorum

